@startuml
title State Diagram - Notification Lifecycle

[*] --> DRAFT : admin creates notification

DRAFT --> PENDING : schedule/send later
DRAFT --> SENT : send immediately
DRAFT --> CANCELLED : cancel draft

PENDING --> SENT : delivery succeeds
PENDING --> FAILED : delivery fails
PENDING --> CANCELLED : cancel pending notification

FAILED --> PENDING : edit and retry
FAILED --> CANCELLED : cancel failed notification

SENT --> SENT : view only\ncontent cannot be edited

SENT --> [*]
CANCELLED --> [*]

note right of SENT
Sent notifications cannot be edited.
They may only be viewed.
end note

note right of FAILED
Admin may edit failed notification
and try again.
end note

@enduml
